Menu
Declare Easy as String
/Easy
 

/MENU
 Open frmMenu
 When btnExit clicked
  Close Program
 When btnDifficulty clicked
  Show frmDifficulty
  If btnMainMenu clicked
    Close frmDifficulty
    Open frmMenu
  If btnEasy clicked
     Difficulty = Easy
  If btnMedium clicked
     Difficulty = Medium
  If btnHard clicked
     Difficulty = Hard
  
  
  
